					<td class="gensmall" width="100%"><div style="float: left;">&nbsp;<b>Post subject:</b> <a href="#p218151">Re: Explanation for how different processor cores are connec</a></div><div style="float: right;"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=218151#p218151"><img src="./styles/subsilver2/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a><b>Posted:</b> Mon May 07, 2018 5:16 pm&nbsp;</div></td>
